originalText.text: Delivered with Dr. B. Robles last Friday at Mount Sinai. It was my first baby, so I had no idea what to expect. What a great experience! Professional, kind, knowledgeable. She makes you feel safe and relaxed during one of the most challenging experiences of your life. God bless and huge THANK YOU from our family.

originalText.text: Dr. Brittany Robles is the best doctor in the city. Before I stated my journey with her, I changed 2 doctors. It was a wonderful journey with her, she was my support system before, during and after my pregnancy. Delivered a baby girl in Jan 2024 in presence of Dr. Robles .

originalText.text: Dr. Robles is awesome! Went in for a consultation and then a few days later, IUD replacement. She does not rush you, welcomes questions and makes you feel so comfortable during these uncomfortable moments! So grateful to have found her and looking forward to future visits, truly!

originalText.text: I am so thankful for Dr. Robles being the OB on call for my delivery. I could not even dream of a more empathetic and positive environment for my induction. She is very professional and knowledgeable, which made me feel safe and comfortable when I was so scared. I will never have enough words to express how much I appreciate having her as my doctor.
